Property taxes are due in 3 days -- but they shouldn’t be. During this national emergency, it is essential Governor Newsom delay the state property tax deadline and provide some relief for hardworking Californians.

It's easy for @HarleyRouda to sit and snipe from the sidelines. Since @HarleyRouda's focus is always on raising taxes, he likely doesn't understand only the governor can move the property tax deadline and only the OC Tax Collector can waive penalties (which I've asked her to do). https://t.co/a66i3gnGhT
While @HarleyRouda hides behind Twitter, I will continue advocating for lower taxes and helping our citizens.
